quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,105,Yaye ngenyaniso Siyithumele (i’Kur’ân) ukanti ngenyaniso Siyithobile kananjalo aSikuthumelanga (nto yimbi) wena ngaphandle kokuba ube ngumvakalisi weendaba ezilungileyo noMlumkisi
  17,106,Kananjalo (le) yi’Kur’ân eSiyahlulahlulileyo khona ukuze uyicengceleze ebantwini kwisithuba eside yaye Siyithumele phantsi amathuba ngamathuba
  17,107,"Yithi: “Kholwani ke kuyo okanye ningakholwa, inene abo babenikwe ulwazi ngaphambili kunayo, xa icengcelezwa kubo, bawa ngobuso babo baqubude"
  17,108,"Ke kaloku bathi, Iphakamile iNkosi yethu inene, isithembiso seNkosi yethu sizalisekile.”"
  17,109,"Baze bawe ngobuso belila, kwaye yona (i’Kur’ân) ibongezelela intobeko"
  17,110,"Yithi: “Bizani kuAllâh okanye kuRahmân (uSolubabalo). Naliphi na (igama) eniMbiza ngalo Yena ngawaKhe (onke) amagama angawona alungileyo.” Ke kaloku ungacengcelezi ngokukhwazakakhuluemthandazweniwakhookanyeuthethele phantsi kakhulu koko funa indlela ephakathi kwezo (zimbini)"
  17,111,"Yithi kwakhona: “Makadunyiswe uAllâh, Ongazanga Wathabatha nyana Engazanga Waba nahlulelane ebukumkanini baKhe, Engenaye namkhuseli wokuMkhusela ebuthathakeni, Mphakamiseni niMenze Mkhulu Yena"
  18,1,Iindumiso mazibe kuAllâh loWo Uthumele iNcwadi (i’Kur’ân kwisiCaka saKhe (uMuhammad) Waza kuyo apho Akenza bugosogoso
  18,2,"Uyenze yathi Tye ukwenzela ukulumkisa ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu, esivela kuYe, Nokunika iindaba zovuyo kumakholwa enza izenzo zobulungisa zokuba okwabo ngumvuzo omhle (iPaladesi)"
  18,3,Baze bahlale apho (ePaladesi) ngonaphakade
  18,4,"Alumkise nabo bathi: “UAllâh Uthabathe (uzele) unyana.”"